text.section:
Notwithstanding Subtitle 2 of this title, this subtitle applies to the establishment of rates for all types of insurance except:
life insurance;
annuities;
health insurance;
marine insurance described in § 11-202(b)(2) of this title;
aircraft insurance described in § 11-202(b)(3)of this title;
reinsurance;
insurance provided under the Maryland Automobile Insurance Fund;
insurance provided under the Chesapeake Employers' Insurance Company;
title insurance;
medical malpractice insurance;
any form or plan of insurance regulated under § 27-217 of this article; and
surety insurance.
